5
00:00:43,440 --> 00:00:47,470
(Vivaldi Music Cafe, 2nd Floor)

6
00:00:48,770 --> 00:00:51,310
(Written by Yang Hee Seung and Kim Bo Ram)

7
00:00:53,850 --> 00:00:56,350
